moduleEncryptionMIB.description: This is a MIB definition for ADVA AG Optical Networking module encryption management.

CryptoFspR7EncryptionReset.name: CryptoFspR7EncryptionReset
CryptoFspR7EncryptionReset.description: Textual-Convention for module 'reset to factory' operation. The rls(1) value means that 'reset to factory' is not happening. Choosing the rtf(2) value executes the 'reset to factory' operation immediately.

CryptoFspR7EncryptionResetCaps.name: CryptoFspR7EncryptionResetCaps

CryptoFspR7EncryptionSwitchCaps.name: CryptoFspR7EncryptionSwitchCaps
CryptoFspR7EncryptionSwitchCaps.description: Textual-Convention for disabling the encrypted mode.

CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchange.name: CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchange
CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchange.description: Textual-Convention for forcing the key exchange process between encryption-capable modules. Successful process startup does not mean that whole operation succeeded.

CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchangeCaps.name: CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchangeCaps
CryptoFspR7ForceKeyExchangeCaps.description: Textual-Convention for forcing the key exchange process between encryption-capable modules. Successful process startup does not mean that whole operation succeeded.
